  <compounddef id="path_8hpp" kind="file" language="C++">
    <compoundname>path.hpp</compoundname>
    <innerclass refid="classhmap_1_1Path" prot="public">hmap::Path</innerclass>
    <innernamespace refid="namespacehmap">hmap</innernamespace>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Path class for manipulating and analyzing paths in 2D space. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="author"><para>Otto Link (<ulink url="mailto:otto.link.bv@gmail.com">otto.link.bv@gmail.com</ulink>) </para>
</simplesect>
This file defines the <computeroutput>Path</computeroutput> class, which extends the <computeroutput>Cloud</computeroutput> class to provide functionalities specific to paths. The <computeroutput>Path</computeroutput> class includes methods for creating, manipulating, and analyzing paths, including smoothing the path with various curves, resampling, and performing operations like meandering and fractalizing.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="version"><para>0.1 </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="date"><para>2023-06-18</para>
